# {DOMAIN} Learn

Make every session improve the system. Run at the end of meaningful work.

## Steps
1. **Decisions.** Log any choice made (what + why + alternatives) to `knowledge-base/decisions/` dated.
2. **Answers.** If a question was answered that could recur, write a canonical FAQ to
   `knowledge-base/faqs/`. If it was answered before, point to the existing one (never twice).
3. **Insights.** Capture reusable explanations/patterns to `knowledge-base/insights/`.
4. **Templatize.** If a deliverable was produced from scratch that will recur, add a template to
   `library/` and note it.
5. **Skill candidates.** If a task was done a 2nd time, propose a new skill (and offer to author +
   repackage).
6. **Update the index.** Keep a running `knowledge-base/README.md` index so future sessions find prior
   learning fast.
7. Report the learnings captured.
